<abstract>
1st Lieutenant, Co. M., 339th Infantry, sent to northern Russia at the end of World War I.
Diary (with transcription) describing war-time activities, 1917-1919; scrapbook of clippings from Detroit and Toledo newspapers 
describing the "Polar Bear" expedition; orders received; photographs; and CD-ROMs of selected items.
</abstract>


